agencies.description: The total number of agencies and trusted agencies created in this account.

agencies_quota.description: The total quota of agencies and trusted agencies that can be created in this account.

attached_policies_per_agency_quota.description: The maximum number of identity policies that can be attached to an agency or trusted agency.

attached_policies_per_group_quota.description: The maximum number of identity policies that can be attached to a user group.

attached_policies_per_user_quota.description: The maximum number of identity policies that can be attached to an IAM user.

groups.description: The current number of user groups created in this account.

groups_quota.description: The quota of user groups that can be created in this account.

policies.description: The current number of custom identity policies created in this account.

policies_quota.description: The maximum number of custom identity policies.

policy_size_quota.description: The maximum number of characters in the policy document of identity policies and trusted policies, excluding spaces.

root_user_mfa_enabled.description: The number of MFA devices enabled for the root user.

users.description: The current number of IAM users created in this account, including the root user.

users_quota.description: The quota of IAM users that can be created in this account, including the root user.

versions_per_policy_quota.description: The maximum number of versions that can be retained for a custom identity policy at the same time.
